title: I don't know if it's frozen or not.
body: When I open up League, I can't launch it because the launch button is black and it was done update patch 6.20

replies.body: All good now, I guess it just needed time.

This issue is a bit unfamiliar to me, would you be able to provide a screenshot?  In general, a black screen can indicate connection issues so the patcher can't download assets.  Go over our [connection issues](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) guide to troubleshoot this.  Let me know the results!
same problem here it was patched but button is black unclickable
